{"tid":629995,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国抗日ドラマ読本　意図せざる反日・愛国コメディ","createTime":"2018-04-15T07:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T14:22:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf97ff358f3686851619214d78f29077f3edfc43","tid":629995,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"なにかと日中両国で話題になる抗日ドラマをユルくカルく紹介している本です。<br />\n『中国抗日ドラマ読本　意図せざる反日・愛国コメディ』（岩田宇伯・著／合同会社パブリブ／2,300円＋税）<br />\n複雑なあらすじをチャート化、登場人物の人脈相関図付きで、初心者でも抗日ドラマが楽しめます。学生服を着た日本軍忍者部隊、意味不明の日本語が書かれた手紙、1930年代中国の設定なのに赤外線レーザーによる不審者検知、ブルーレイによる生体認証など、ツッコミどころ満載の抗日ドラマを存分に楽しみましょう！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/154645_1899e5f39916351bb940d5068c37159b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F154645_1899e5f39916351bb940d5068c37159b.png&h=4899594d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d35414961a73908002e6c3ec373c71ab7536eef8","tid":629995,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"有冇徒手撕開既橋段？"},{"pid":"bb73d2eabed10b8ffce0be5348369666629a0f25","tid":629995,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:58:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156170242712357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10156170242712357&d=f8iRq13rN6MEZzm0wnae075jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=461c86ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10156170242712357</a>"},{"pid":"796fd8d13d3c580bfcb197fbaa64f1b4249be8ff","tid":629995,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:01:38.000Z","msg":"變笑片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b688be3576e36c1165f8e02b239dff3ce66581ac","tid":629995,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T